7ï¸âƒ£ Checking If a Year Is a Leap Year
--------------------------------------------------
Scanner Class for User Input:
- Scanner sc = new Scanner(System.in); â†’ Takes an integer input for the year.

Leap Year Conditions:
- Divisible by 4 â†’ It may be a leap year.
- Divisible by 100 â†’ It must also be divisible by 400 to be a leap year.
- Divisible by 400 â†’ It is a leap year.

Key Learning:
- % (modulus operator) helps determine divisibility.
- Nested if-else conditions help check multiple dependent conditions.

Edge Cases Handled:
âœ… Leap Years:
- 1600, 2000, 2020, 2024 (divisible by 400 or by 4 but not 100).

âŒ Not Leap Years:
- 1700, 1800, 1900, 2100 (divisible by 100 but not by 400).

ðŸ”¹ Normal Years:
- 2017, 2018, 2019, 2021 (not divisible by 4).

Closing the Scanner:
- sc.close(); â†’ Closes the scanner to avoid memory leaks.

